Joe Stecher https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Stecher 0 Joe Stecher (April 4, 1893 – March 29, 1974), sometimes spelled Joe Stetcher, was a professional wrestler and three-time World Heavyweight Wrestling Champion. Stecher is the first professional wrestler to regain the original version of the World Heavyweight Wrestling Championship.
